  <name>Workout Timer</name>
  <summary>Round timer and workout planner</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A sport training application for Linux. Features a configurable round timer
      with pause periods and audio alerts, and a training plan builder where you can
      create plans with timed exercises and rep-based movements.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Configurable round timer with adjustable rounds, duration, and pause</li>
      <li>Training plan builder with timed and rep-based exercises</li>
      <li>Built-in exercise database with 873 exercises and images</li>
      <li>8 pre-built default training plans</li>
      <li>Training history with per-exercise logging</li>
      <li>Customizable sound effects for different events</li>
      <li>Fullscreen mode for workout sessions</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer id="io.github.NikolausB">
